Author: dostoyefski
Text: CAHMS are complete and utter trash. They discharged me for “not cooperating” because my mental health issues were too bad for me to look my therapist in the eye, let alone talk to them. It’s even worse now I’m over 18, went to my GP and was told it’s a 2.5 year wait for counselling. Everything fricking sucks y’all. I hope things get better for you!!
